---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="IEP Help at Home | Rabbia Psychologist NeuroCare"
  description="Get IEP assistance at home, prepare for school meetings, understand teacher concerns, and turn school confusion into practical support steps for your child."
>
  <div class="bg-brand-cream py-16 lg:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-6">From IEP Confusion to a Clear Support Plan</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
        Understand the meeting, prepare the right questions, and turn school concerns into practical next steps for your child.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-4xl space-y-12">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">School concerns parents bring</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Parents often contact us when they feel overwhelmed by school feedback, confused by IEP terminology, or unsure how to address their child's classroom behavior.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">IEP and school meeting preparation</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We help you organize your thoughts, understand the proposed goals, and prepare to advocate effectively for your child's needs during school meetings.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Questions to ask teachers</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We provide you with specific, constructive questions to ask educators to gain a clearer picture of your child's day-to-day experience.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Understanding school feedback</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We translate educational jargon and teacher reports into clear developmental insights.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Behaviour concerns at school</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">If your child is struggling behaviorally in the classroom, we help create strategies that can be coordinated between home and school.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Learning and attention concerns</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Guidance on how to approach suspected ADHD or learning difficulties within the educational system.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Report review before school meetings</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">We can review external therapy or assessment reports with you to determine how best to present them to the school team.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-4">Parent-school communication plan</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Developing a structured, positive approach to communicating with teachers and school administrators.</p>
      </section>

      <div class="mt-12 text-center">
        <a href="/book" class="inline-block px-8 py-4 bg-brand-navy text-white rounded-lg font-bold text-lg hover:bg-blue-900 transition-all shadow-lg">
          Book Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
